    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you need capture output</p>\n\n<pre><code>StringWriter sw = new StringWriter();\nnew Throwable(\"\").printStackTrace(new PrintWriter(sw));\nString stackTrace = sw.toString();\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 313216,
      "reputation" : 47819,
      "user_id" : 627727,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 84,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/uOIWL.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "mkobit",
